<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_03_IH_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema511_01.css" /> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_03_ih_0007 paging">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7_orange" class="is_star2" lang="y">직육면체의 부피가 480 cm³일 때, 높이는 몇 cm인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3>새로 만든 직육면체의 부피는 처음 직육면체의 부피의 몇 배인가요?</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_03_IH/616_03_07.png" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="box_cm">
              <span class="cm1">2cm</span>
              <span class="cm2">4cm</span>
              <span class="cm3">3cm</span>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area mt_30">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="10" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>배</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y"></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>직육면체의 가로, 세로, 높이를 각각 3배로 늘이면 부피는 3×3×3=27(배)가 됩니다.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3>새로 만든 직육면체의 부피는 몇 cm³인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_03_IH/616_03_07.png" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="box_cm_secondpage">
              <span class="cm1">2cm</span>
              <span class="cm2">4cm</span>
              <span class="cm3">3cm</span>
            </div>

            <div class="input_area mt_30">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="10" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>cm³</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y"></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>(처음 직육면체의 부피)= 3×4×2=24 (cm³)</li>
                    <li>(새로 만든 직육면체의 부피)= 24×27=648 (cm³)</li>
                    <li>
                      <span class="solve_img">다른풀이</span>
                      새로 만든 직육면체의 가로는3×3=9(cm), 세로는 4×3=12 (cm), 높이는 2×3=6 (cm)이므로 부피는 9×12×6=648 (cm³)입니다.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
